= open 'god helmet' project


URL = http://open-rtms.sourceforge.net/ [http://technoccult.net/archives/2010/03/04/open-source-god-helmet-project/]

=Description=

"Transcranial Magnetic Stimulation (TMS) is the application of variable magnetic fields to the brain. Research has indicated that rTMS (repeating TMS pulses, or repetitive TMS) may have effects as diverse as treatment of depression, pain releif, feelings of euphoria or fear, and altered states of consciousness such as out-of-body experiences. A recent television program even showed potential uses in warfare and defense. This project focuses on the use of low intensity magnetic fields similar in strength[pdf] to those from a hair dryer."


